# MD in LAMMPS

## two component system

American Journal of Physics **88**, 401 (2020); doi: 10.1119/10.0000654

### L-J Potential

#### Script

```shell
#KALJ NVE, read data
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p #periodic boundary cond.in each direction
region my_region block 0 9.4 0 9.4 0 9.4
create_box 2 my_region
create_atoms 1 random 800 229609 my_region
create_atoms 2 random 200 691203 my_region
mass 1 1
mass 2 1
velocity all create 0.5 92561 dist gaussian # T = 0.5

pair_style lj/cut 2.5 # Define interaction potential
pair_coeff 1 1 1.0 1.0 2.5 #type type eps sigma rcut
pair_coeff 1 2 1.5 0.80 2.0 #typeA typeB epsAB sigmaAB rcutAB = 2.5*0:8 = 2.0
pair_coeff 2 2 0.5 0.88 2.2 #typeB typeB epsBB sigmaBB rcutBB = 2.5*0.88 = 2.2
timestep 0.005 #Delta t
neighbor 0.3 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes
dump 1 all custom 50 confdump.*.data id type x y z vx vy vz
dump_modify 1 sort id
dump 2 all custom 50 vmd.lammpstrj id type x y z
# set numerical integrator
minimize 1.0e-4 1.0e-6 100 1000
fix nve1 all nve # NVE; default is velocity verlet

compute rdfAABBAB all rdf 25 1 1 2 2 1 2
fix myrdf all ave/time 25 8 200 c_rdfAABBAB[*] file gofrAABBAB.data mode vector

run 1000
```

### WCA Potential

#### Script

```sh
#KAWCA NVE, read data
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p #periodic boundary cond.in each direction
region my_region block 0 9.4 0 9.4 0 9.4
create_box 2 my_region
create_atoms 1 random 800 229609 my_region
create_atoms 2 random 200 691203 my_region
mass 1 1
mass 2 1
velocity all create 0.5 92561 dist gaussian

pair_style cosine/squared 1.1224 # Define interaction potential
pair_coeff 1 1 1.0 1.0 1.1224 wca #type type eps sigma rcut
pair_coeff 1 2 1.5 0.80 0.8979 wca #typeA typeB epsAB sigmaAB rcutAB
pair_coeff 2 2 0.5 0.88 0.9877 wca #typeB typeB epsBB sigmaBB rcutBB
timestep 0.005 #Delta t
neighbor 0.3 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes
dump 1 all custom 50 confdump.*.data id type x y z vx vy vz
dump_modify 1 sort id
dump 2 all custom 50 vmd.lammpstrj id type x y z
# set numerical integrator
minimize 1.0e-4 1.0e-6 100 1000
fix nve1 all nve # NVE; default is velocity verlet

compute rdfAABBAB all rdf 25 1 1 2 2 1 2
fix myrdf all ave/time 25 8 200 c_rdfAABBAB[*] file gofrAABBAB.data mode vector

run 1000
```

## Five component system

NATURE COMMUNICATIONS| (2018) 9:3272 | DOI: 10.1038/s41467-018-05371-6 

![截屏2022-12-22 00.04.58](image/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-12-22%2000.04.58.png)

### Script

```sh
# phi = 0.532
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p #periodic boundary cond.in each direction
region my_region block 0 20.010304993635273 0 20.010304993635273 0 20.010304993635273
create_box 5 my_region
create_atoms 1 random 200 5 my_region
create_atoms 2 random 200 7 my_region
create_atoms 3 random 200 9 my_region
create_atoms 4 random 200 11 my_region
create_atoms 5 random 200 13 my_region
mass 1 1
mass 2 1
mass 3 1
mass 4 1
mass 5 1
velocity all create 0.000181 92561 dist gaussian # T = 0.000181

pair_style cosine/squared 1.1224 # Define interaction potential
pair_coeff * * 1.0 1.0 1.1224 wca #initialize the potential
pair_coeff 1 1 1.0 0.8888 0.8888 wca #type type eps sigma rcut
pair_coeff 2 2 1.0 0.95733 0.95733 wca #type type eps sigma rcut
pair_coeff 3 3 1.0 1.0 1.0 wca #type type eps sigma rcut
pair_coeff 4 4 1.0 1.04267 1.04267 wca #type type eps sigma rcut
pair_coeff 5 5 1.0 1.112 1.112 wca #type type eps sigma rcut
timestep 0.005 #Delta t
neighbor 0.3 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes
dump 1 all custom 1000 conf/confdump.*.data id type x y z vx vy vz
dump_modify 1 sort id
dump 2 all custom 1000 vmd.lammpstrj id type x y z
dump 3 all xyz 1000 out.xyz
# set numerical integrator
minimize 1.0e-4 1.0e-6 100 1000 # etol ftol maxiter maxeval
fix nve1 all nve # NVE; default is velocity verlet

run 1000000
```
